  <description type="morphology">Leaf blades narrowly ovate or elliptical, 45--67 &amp;#180; 15--22 cm. Inflorescences erect, 11--23 &amp;#180; 5--10 cm; bracts of main axis whitish proximally, green (proximal bracts) or pink (distal bracts) distally; proximal bracts ovate to rectangular, deeply saccate, 4--4.5 &amp;#180; 4 cm, apex obtuse or truncate-apiculate; distal bracts narrowly ovate, 8--9 &amp;#180; 4--4.5 cm, apex rounded. Flowers: perianth white or spotted with purple; staminodes pale yellow with yellow streak down center of lip.</description>
